    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly-<br />I mentioned last week that I discovered your blog last summer and that, with time on my hands at the moment, I was going to start reading from the first post. I just wanted to let you know how much I&#39;m loving your writing and your RECIPES! This week I made the whole wheat bread from the ranch (amazing toasted with a little apricot jam!), the zucchini frittata (got a little sloppy when I tried to flip, so think I&#39;ll stick to putting it under the broiler for the last few minutes), the &#8220;french-style&#8221; scrambled eggs were the creamiest I&#39;ve ever had, and currently my apartment smells AMAZING as I impatiently wait for these pistachio-apricot oatmeal cookies to crispen up! Thanks so much! I&#39;m so thrilled that I still have YEARS of your posts left to read and I can&#39;t wait to choose my next recipe!<br />~Katie</p>
